# The API half of the full-stack example. Plain runtime config; no build step.
#
# DATABASE_URL is injected by Dockhold when you enable the managed database
# add-on — don't set it yourself, just read it (see db.js).
#
# ALLOWED_ORIGIN: the deployed web app's URL, so the browser is allowed to call
# this API (CORS). Set it after you deploy the web app, then redeploy.
#   ALLOWED_ORIGIN=https://fullstack-web-xxxx.dockhold.app
#
# PORT is provided by Dockhold at runtime.
